      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you'll say that but it doesn't feel true. like, how am i supposed to face the people i know? how do i even wake up tomorrow knowing everything is gone? it just feels like i've reached the end of the road. i'm already at the bottom, i might as well just stay here.",
